Your personal information
All collection and processing of Personal Information shall be done in accordance with VG’s Privacy Notice.
Your driving behaviour
The App collects information about your driving behaviour, which is used to determine your driving score. This score is used to reward you with an Active Reward.
In order for us to collect your driving information, your mobile phone must be switched on, the location setting on your phone must be on, you must be registered in the App, your mobile data must be switched on, and you must have cellular data connectivity.
What data charges can I expect when using the app?
The App will automatically attempt to upload your driving information after each trip. This upload can be done through Wi-Fi or mobile data. If an upload fails, the App will automatically attempt to upload again after your next trip. You can manage these upload options in the App’s Settings. Any data usage, including downloading and updating the App, will be charged to you at normal network provider rates.
Can I download the App on any handset?
The App is available for iOS and most Android operating systems. A list of compatible devices can be provided on request.
To download the App from the App Store, you need have a registered App Store or Google Play Store account.
Note: If you change smartphones, you’ll be able to reinstall and continue using the App.
Registration and eligibility
You are solely responsible for all activity that occurs on your App profile and for maintaining the confidentiality of your App profile. Anyone with whom you share your phone may access the App installed on your phone, your App registration details, your driving score and your past trip information.
You are responsible for keeping these details private and for carefully vetting the persons with whom you share your phone and the information on your phone.
Note that if you connect with other users or an additional user on the App during the POC period those users will be able to view your driving score. Neither VG nor the Discovery Group will be responsible for any unauthorised disclosure by such users of your driving score or any consequences resulting from such disclosure.
