Scoring and Rewards
Your mobile data and GPS need to be switched on and the App activated for your trips to be eligible for purposes of the Drive Programme. Only trips that record all the relevant data will qualify towards Active Rewards.
Your trips will be recorded daily and Active Rewards earned will reflect the following week.
The way in which driving scores are calculated and Active Rewards are earned is determined by VG from time to time and may be amended by VG in its sole and absolute discretion.
